---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="SocialProof vs HubSpot — Testimonial Collection vs CRM | SocialProof"
  description="HubSpot is a CRM. SocialProof is a testimonial tool. See why using the right tool for each job beats trying to make HubSpot collect testimonials."
>
  <main class="vs-page">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="eyebrow">SocialProof vs HubSpot</p>
        <h1>HubSpot manages relationships. We capture proof.</h1>
        <div class="cta-group">
          <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn btn-primary">Try SocialProof free</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="intro">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="lead">HubSpot is an excellent CRM and marketing platform. But it's not designed to collect, moderate, and display customer testimonials on your website. You can hack together a workflow — form + feedback + a copy-paste process — but it's not purpose-built. SocialProof does one job exceptionally well: help you collect testimonials via a shareable link, approve them, and embed them beautifully on your site.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="comparison-table">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Feature comparison</h2>
        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Feature</th>
              <th>HubSpot</th>
              <th>SocialProof</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td>Purpose</td><td>CRM / Marketing automation</td><td>Testimonial collection & display</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Shareable testimonial collect link</td><td>⚠️ Possible with custom forms</td><td>✅ Built-in, one click</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Approval workflow for testimonials</td><td>❌ Not a native feature</td><td>✅ Yes — built-in moderation</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Embeddable widget for your site</td><td>❌ Requires custom development</td><td>✅ One script tag</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Price to start</td><td>Free CRM (limited), paid starts $15/mo/user</td><td>✅ Free forever for 1 active widget</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Price for full features</td><td>$800+/mo for Marketing Hub</td><td>$9/mo Pro</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Built for small business solo operators</td><td>⚠️ Designed for larger teams</td><td>✅ Yes — setup in under 10 min</td></tr>

          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="verdict">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>The honest verdict</h2>
        <p>Use HubSpot for CRM, email marketing, and sales pipelines. Use SocialProof to collect and display customer testimonials. They're complementary — SocialProof even embeds on HubSpot-hosted pages.</p>
        <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn btn-primary">Start free — no credit card</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>
